div.p:
There appear to be several alternatives on future courses of action short of an
                    actual initiative. We could: 

—(1) explore the subject with the GVN;

—(2) develop more detailed political/ceasefire scenarios;



—(3) move the issue to a final decision, perhaps at the NSC level, on the assumption that, while
                            the uncertainties are great, they are not going to diminish;
